        "id": 1002539
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-02-22T20:56:26Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Note that existence of this cache implies that changing \"project -\u003e service account\" association in the projets.cfg will take up to 1h to propagate everywhere fully (until all cached tokens are evicted).\n\nWe may want to document it in project.cfg proto.\n\nIf it becomes an issue, there are ways to introduce cache invalidation without sacrificing performance, but this is not trivial. Note that this cache is pretty important to avoid hammering Token Server on all RPCs, so we can\u0027t just remove it. Though we can evict tokens from the cache earlier (e.g. 15 min).",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 139,
        "startChar": 1,
        "endLine": 139,
        "endChar": 9
      },
      "revId": "1c805a9fa5bff311021bbad66db8ce4ee0c349c7",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": false
    },
